'''CIVO United Football Club''' (CIVO Utd) is a [[Malawi]]an [[football (soccer)]] club based in [[Lilongwe]] and currently plays in the [[TNM Super League]]  the top division of [[Malawi]]an [[football]].
<ref>http://it.soccerway.com/teams/malawi/civo-united/6613/matches/</ref>

In 1987 the team has won the [[TNM Super League]].

==Stadium==
Currently the team plays at the [[Civo Stadium]].

